message: The former edits contained misleading, irrelevant, and false information (i.e. the claim that Clay Olsen graduated from Brigham Young University, although he never attended BYU) and the citations were based on opinion pieces. I added the mission statement as stated by the organization itself and deleted the false and irrelevant information.
Removed information that could have been seen as "reading like an advertisement." Pulled directly from the organization's website for edit.
Edit made to provide better sources.
minor edits some small word changes to sound less like advertising
Mostly grammar and one word clarification to simplify descriptions.
